summary:
I like developing apps that people love to use. I have worked in multiple startups as an Android developer and built their applications from scratch. I recently moved to Vienna from Singapore to work with Bitpanda and help them achieve their goal of making investing accessible for everyone.

I publish my personal projects under the name Code My Brains Out. My apps have more than 6,000,000 downloads on Google Play.
My areas of interest include Connected Cars, AI, IoT, and Drones.

Skills: Kotlin, Java, Android SDK, Apps for Android Wear devices, App UI/UX, JSON/RESTful communications, XML
